  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为金融科技系统画一个完整的交易风控流程图。起点应该是AuthVault，也就是身份认证中心，所有请求都从那里进来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，AuthVault作为入口节点。接下来应该连到哪里？是直接进入支付网关吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "不，中间必须过一道风控。AuthVault之后要接FraudDetection，这是我们的欺诈检测模块，先做一次初筛。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，AuthVault指向FraudDetection。然后FraudDetection的输出应该有个判断节点吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，这里需要第一个PaymentGateway判断节点，菱形的那种。初筛通过的就进TransactionQueue排队，没通过的直接打回PaymentGateway做拒绝处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，您说的是FraudDetection之后接一个PaymentGateway判断，然后分两支：Yes走TransactionQueue，No走另一个PaymentGateway？这两个PaymentGateway是同一个模块的不同状态，还是不同的节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_FraudDetection",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue"
