      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是同一个模块，但No分支那个是拒绝处理的终态，用方框表示；判断节点用菱形。TransactionQueue出来之后还要再过一次PaymentGateway判断，这是第二层风控。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，TransactionQueue后面接第二个PaymentGateway判断节点。这层判断如果No的话，是回到TransactionQueue重新排队吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，No分支回到TransactionQueue，Yes分支继续往下走第三层判断。我们设计了三层风控，每层都是PaymentGateway判断。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "三层风控，明白了。第二层Yes走第三层PaymentGateway判断，这层No的话也是回TransactionQueue？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，第三层如果No还是回队列，Yes的话这次才真正进入最终的PaymentGateway处理节点，然后到LedgerService记账。",
